Base object types with ego properties <p>
<ol>
<li>
<a href="#head-2473e96bc614a911821242119918a241a41836d6">Introduction</a></li>
<li>
<a href="#head-21d278837034557e7a9b46210d42d6e7b8075142">Terminology</a></li>
<li>
<a href="#head-f32d0645a8333f8a2fde36f8bf8e7f5d041c3cdb">Weapons</a></li>
<ol>
<li>
<a href="#head-ce3f44c0310cdcac9a2b874f60bdda88088ad185">Swords</a></li>
<li>
<a href="#head-fe711a0da33b4859e18ea633d65f0b4537798528">Hafted weapons</a></li>
<li>
<a href="#head-add8329d9620426865f5157440fc550b74d56675">Polearms</a></li>
